title: Stukas - Luftwaffe drama-documentary
description:
One of the world's most dramatic and controversial air battle movies. A docu-drama about the legendary Stuka airplane and its equally legendary pilots. 

Year make: 1941

No subtitles, German speech.

runtime approx: 96 minutes

Quality is good for being an ww2 reel.

Btw this one doesnt work to play in VLC player it needs to be burned on a DVD.

Enjoy!
